init_text: When you're 28, science discovers a drug that stops all effects of aging, creating immortality. Your government decides to give the drug to all citizens under 26, but you and the rest of the "Lost Generations" are deemed too high-risk. When you're 85, the side effects are finally discovered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: paranoia, schizophrenia, and a complete inability to distinguish between fantasy and reality.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: as you age backwards, your mental state will also age backwards.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It is later discovered that the drug was (in part) created by a mad scientist who is now dead, and it was his intention to destroy society

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The cure is a drink that must be taken at exactly midnight of the person's birthday.
